title: Video: No longer business as usual as Qualtrough heads to Ottawa
text: Video: No longer business as usual as Qualtrough heads to Ottawa You will notice an immediate change in the way the federal Liberals do business as they take the reigns of power in Ottawa, says newly elected Delta MP Carla Qualtrough. She expects the Liberals to deliver on their campaign message of change.
